E

Event - Class in se.rupy.http
Asynchronous HTTP request/response, this virtually represents a client socket, but in the case where the server is behind a proxy we cannot expect to see that representation since sockets will be reused by multiple different external clients, it's a performance tradeoff that we gladly accept since hiding behind an Apache or some other proxy is this server probable use.
exit(Session, int) - Method in class se.rupy.http.Service
